  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Purpose of the investigators study is to determine the short and medium term histological
      cancer control of focal therapy using MR-guided focal laser ablation therapy in the treatment
      of localised prostate cancer.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
